chart.programText:
A = data('conviva.quality_metriclens.total_attempts', filter=(not filter('Show', 'Unknown')), extrapolation='zero').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('conviva.quality_metriclens.plays_percent', filter=(not filter('Show', 'Unknown')), extrapolation='zero').scale(0.01).publish(label='B', enable=False)
E = (A*B).publish(label='E', enable=False)
J = (E).mean(over='1m').publish(label='J', enable=False)
K = (E).timeshift('30m').mean(over='1m').publish(label='K', enable=False)
L = (J-K).above(0).top(count=10).publish(label='L', enable=False)
M = ((L/J)*100).mean(by=['Show']).publish(label='M')
